  "description": "<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201305/ca59b3e726274f518deae8f099b9af1a.jpg\" style=\"border-right-width: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; margin-left: 5px; border-left-width: 0px; margin-right: 5px;\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t《英文天天写》是沪江社团一档写作类社刊，其目的在于提升大家的英语写作能力。每期节目主持人都会给出一个话题，积极参加的童鞋还会得到主持人的专业点评哦！想提高英语写作的童鞋千万不要错过哦！<a href=\"http://pass.hujiang.com/signup/?source=en_sqyd&amp;url=http://st.hujiang.com/mag/135231930/\" style=\"color: rgb(0,90,148); text-decoration: none;\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201304/d5e293c817a6488d819f0c13a95230e1.jpg\" style=\"line-height: 1.8em; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; margin-left: 5px; border-left-width: 0px; margin-right: 5px;\" /></a>去沪江社团订阅本社刊！</p>\n<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i3.s.7.hjfile.cn/entry/201601/c65a29cb-3dad-4a3b-bf5d-f2b92294a244.jpg\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 28px; width: 500px; font-family: 'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; height: 279px; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 15px;\" /><span style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 28px; font-family: 'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 28px; font-family: 'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 28px; font-family: 'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 28px; font-family: 'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 28px; font-family: 'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 28px; font-family: 'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>话题：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tWriting: imagine a scenario or express your opinion<br />\n\tGain<br />\n\tTo gain means to obtain more. What is gained? How is it gained? Who is gaining?<br />\n\tThis week's topic: They gain an opportunity... (90-110 words)</p>\n<p>\n\tSuggestions:<br />\n\t1) gain experience<br />\n\t2) calculating the gain<br />\n\t3) gain a profit<br />\n\t4) gain an advantage<br />\n\t5) Instead of writing a scenario, feel free to comment on the story below.</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>范例1：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tHe had to gain access to the neuroscience department database. More specifically, he had to get to the private drive of the department. Doug had tried to gain access through different computers located in the chemistry department, as it was much easier and safer for him to work with the computers there. It took him a little while, but he had no problem getting into the general database of the neuroscience department. The private drive, however, was a different matter. Despite his best effort, he could not even see the hidden drive.</p>\n<p>\n\t想要得到专业主持人的点评和意见吗？<a href=\"http://st.hujiang.com/topic/167011978378/\" target=\"_blank\">快来节目现场一试身手吧&gt;&gt;</a></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p768182/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p768182\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin